room_title: Escape room "Aunt Bea’s Cabin" by Escape Room Alexandria in Alexandria (MN)
room_description: Your favorite, adventurous Aunt Bea suddenly passed away. Before she died, she sent you a postcard saying she has three valuable treasures cleverly hidden inside her Alexandria lake cabin. Her estranged business partner is heading that way - to take the items for herself. Do you have what it takes to find your Aunt Bea’s treasures? Work together quickly in 60 minutes to find them before it is too late!
